, 
<figureCitation id="131E2A6BFF97FFE1FCC56985E506FB82" box="[809,841,1008,1034]" captionStart="FIGURES 30–36" captionStartId="12.[150,271,1898,1922]" captionTargetBox="[154,1435,203,1857]" captionTargetId="figure-61@12.[150,1436,194,1877]" captionTargetPageId="12" captionText="FIGURES 30–36. Longibeccus fuscovittatus (Ricardo), male wing and terminalia. 30. Right wing; 31–33. Lateral, dorsal and ventral views; 34. Gonostylus; 35–36. Aedeagus, dorsal and lateral views. Abbr.: r4, m3=cells; cerc=cercus; epand=epandrium; epiph= epiphallus; goncx=gonocoxite; hypd=hypandrium; pvapod=posteroventral aedeagal apodeme." pageId="11" pageNumber="12">30</figureCitation>
, 
